Package: POPSR
Type: Package
Title: R Interface of POPS
Version: 3.2.2
Authors@R: c(person("Jens", "Kleinjung", role  = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                     email = "jens@jkleinj.eu"),
             person("Franca", "Fraternali", role  = c("aut", "cph"),
                     email = "franca.fraternali@kcl.ac.uk"))
Author: Jens Kleinjung, Franca Fraternali
Maintainer: Jens Kleinjung <jens@jkleinj.eu> 
Description: The package serves as a front-end to the POPS program,
  either in the R environment (pops.R) or as a Shiny server (shiny.R).
  It serves additionally as a source for SASA plotting functions
  (plotSASA.R) and to process protein complexes on-the-fly in the
  spirit of POPSCOMP.
Depends: R (>= 3.5),
		 bio3d (>= 2.3),
		 ggplot2 (>= 3.2),
		 rgl (>= 0.1),
		 optparse (>= 1.6.6)
Imports: 
Suggests: knitr,
          rmarkdown
Collate: popscomp.R plotSASA.R runApp.R
